flowchart TD
    Main[main branch] -->|cut hotfix| Hotfix[hotfix branch]
    Hotfix -->|bug fixed| MergeHotfixMain[Merge into main]
    Hotfix -->|sync fix| MergeHotfixDev[Merge into develop]
    MergeHotfixMain --> TagMain[Tag release on main]

    Main -->|cut release| Release[release branch]
    Release -->|stabilize| BugfixRelease[Commit bug fixes only]
    BugfixRelease --> MergeRelMain[Merge into main]
    BugfixRelease --> MergeRelDev[Merge into develop]
    MergeRelMain --> TagRelease[Tag version on main]

    Develop[develop branch] -->|cut feature| Feature[feature branch]
    Feature -->|implement| Commits[Commit feature work]
    Commits -->|PR approved| MergeFeature[Merge into develop]
    MergeFeature --> Develop
    Develop -->|ready for release| Release
